data.description: Fantastic home within the gated Stonegate community at Johnson Ranch. Situated on a corner lot in a cul-de-sac street. New HVAC & Water Heater! HVAC replaced in 2020 & Water heater replaced 2022. Kitchen is spacious & inviting, boasting a gas range/oven, kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, & granite countertops. The master bedroom is generously sized with two closets & vaulted ceilings. Built-in cabinets in the garage offer additional storage, for a refrigerator/freezer & pre plumber for water softener.  Step outside to a sizable backyard complete with a covered patio, providing an excellent space for outdoor enjoyment. Johnson Ranch community offers a wealth of amenities for you to enjoy. Location is both convenient & desirable, with shopping & schools in close proximity. A notable bonus is the fully paid solar system, which enhances energy efficiency and savings. This charming home is move-in ready, waiting for you to make it your own.
